  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2081860/extras/0615c8a5b80bfa628cd5102fa2f4c492.poster.avif?t=1682110978\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2081860/extras/0615c8a5b80bfa628cd5102fa2f4c492.webm?t=1682110978\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><strong>The Van Game</strong> is a retro style road-trip around the USA, inspired by the classic \"Oregon Trail\". Discover over a dozen national parks the way they're meant to be seen, in glorious pixel-art!  Dozens of Choose-Your-Own-Adventure encounters with police, Crazy Karens, and fellow travelers. Play 7 different mini-games and manage your resources to stay on the road. Contract over 12 diseases and try to keep your crew happy!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2081860/extras/69d9def8a05acfa1803c3bf6698bed61.poster.avif?t=1682110978\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2081860/extras/69d9def8a05acfa1803c3bf6698bed61.webm?t=1682110978\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2081860/extras/69d9def8a05acfa1803c3bf6698bed61.mp4?t=1682110978\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>14 beautiful national parks to explore<br></li><li>12 fun-filled illnesses including everyones favorite, dysentery!<br></li><li>7 challenging mini-games<br></li><li>Manage your money, food, gas and more<br></li><li>Keep your crew happy or they might just abandon the van life<br></li><li>Upgrade and customize your van, your home away from home<br></li><li>Collect stamps in your park passport and maybe even learn a little</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2081860/extras/d0f303e2bdbeff417b15a796f78701cc.poster.avif?t=1682110978\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2081860/extras/d0f303e2bdbeff417b15a796f78701cc.webm?t=1682110978\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
