sport and maybe even learn a little</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2081860/extras/d0f303e2bdbeff417b15a796f78701cc.poster.avif?t=1682110978\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2081860/extras/d0f303e2bdbeff417b15a796f78701cc.webm?t=1682110978\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
